```plantuml
@startuml geovanegodoi_MicroServicesPOC

actor User

participant "Catalog Microservice" as Catalog
participant "Customer Microservice" as Customer
participant "Order Microservice" as Order
database "MongoDB (Catalog)" as CatalogDB
database "MongoDB (Customer)" as CustomerDB
database "MongoDB (Order)" as OrderDB
queue "RabbitMQ" as RabbitMQ

User -> Catalog: Create Catalog Item
Catalog -> CatalogDB: Save Catalog Item
Catalog -> RabbitMQ: Publish CatalogItemCreated

User -> Customer: Create Customer
Customer -> CustomerDB: Save Customer
Customer -> RabbitMQ: Publish CustomerUpdated

User -> Order: Create Order
Order -> OrderDB: Save Order
Order -> RabbitMQ: Publish OrderCreated

RabbitMQ -> Catalog: Consume OrderCreated
Catalog -> CatalogDB: Update Item Orders

RabbitMQ -> Customer: Consume OrderCreated
Customer -> CustomerDB: Update Customer Order History

@enduml
```